#SmartAgro Backend

REST API built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB for managing Categories, Products, and Orders.

Features

CRUD for Categories

CRUD for Products

CRUD for Orders

Clean REST API structure

CORS enabled for frontend access

JSON request body parsing

Centralized error handling

